OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780585868
OL,3,CWW2 bomb found in construction site
OL,4,Csafely detonated
OL,6,FAn unexploded Second World War bomb
OL,7,Fdiscovered at a construction site in
OL,8,FCoventry has been safely detonated.
OL,10,FThe device was found on Tuesday at
OL,11,Faround 2.55pm at a construction site
OL,12,Fin Radford at the Sandy Lane Business
OL,13,FPark.
OL,15,FA 100-metre cordon was in place as
OL,16,Fhomes were evacuated as emergency
OL,17,Fservices and the council worked to
OL,18,Fremove the bomb.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
