OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780585868
OL,3,CWW2 bomb found in construction site
OL,4,Csafely detonated
OL,6,FNearly 100 homes were evacuated whilst
OL,7,Fwork was carried out. The cordon is
OL,8,Fnow lifted for residents to return
OL,9,Fhome.
OL,11,FPolice said bomb disposal teams
OL,12,Fperformed a "controlled detonation of
OL,13,Fthe fuze earlier this evening and the
OL,14,Fsubsequent safe removal of the bomb".
OL,16,FAssistant Chief Constable Mike O'Hara,
OL,17,Ffrom West Midlands Police, said: "Our
OL,18,Fapproach throughout has been to keep
OL,19,Feveryone safe while minimising
OL,20,Fdisruption to the local community.
OL,26,@yD@bOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780585868
OL,3,CWW2 bomb found in construction site
OL,4,Csafely detonated
OL,6,F"Coventry City Council has provided
OL,7,Fsignificant support to displaced
OL,8,Fresidents and worked closely with
OL,9,Fpartners to ensure people had access
OL,10,Fto accommodation and welfare support.
OL,12,F"Thanks to EOD's expertise and the
OL,13,Fdynamic render safe planning the
OL,14,Fcordon was kept to a minimum of 100
OL,15,Fmetres, preventing a much wider
OL,16,Fevacuation and limiting disruption to
OL,17,Fhomes and businesses. Col Nick Handy
OL,18,Fcommended all his soldiers for their
OL,19,Fefforts.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780585868
OL,3,CWW2 bomb found in construction site
OL,4,Csafely detonated
OL,6,F"I would like to thank everyone for
OL,7,Ftheir co-operation and support over
OL,8,Fthe last day to bring this to a safe
OL,9,Fconclusion."
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Fire Officer Richard
OL,12,FStanton said: "Coventry Fire Station
OL,13,Fwas designated as the official
OL,14,Frendezvous point for the operation,
OL,15,Fproviding a central and secure
OL,16,Flocation for emergency responders and
OL,17,Fpartner organisations to coordinate
OL,18,Factivity and maintain situational
OL,19,Fawareness.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]tD@OOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1780585868
OL,3,CWW2 bomb found in construction site
OL,4,Csafely detonated
OL,6,F"Its close proximity to the detonation
OL,7,Fsite proved invaluable. The station
OL,8,Foffered a safe and accessible base for
OL,9,Foperational briefings, welfare
OL,10,Fsupport, and rest and recovery,
OL,11,Fenabling personnel from multiple
OL,12,Fagencies to work together effectively
OL,13,Fthroughout the incident.
OL,15,F"We would like to thank everyone
OL,16,Finvolved in making these arrangements
OL,17,Fpossible. The successful outcome
OL,18,Freflects the professionalism,
OL,19,Fcooperation and shared commitment of
OL,20,Fall those who worked to protect and
OL,21,Fsupport the local community."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU}D@]O]
